flowchart LR
    A([User opens app]) --> B{Logged in?}
    B -->|No| C[Login Page]
    C --> D[POST /api/auth/login]
    D --> E{Valid credentials?}
    E -->|No| F[Show error]
    F --> C
    E -->|Yes| G[Store JWT in localStorage]
    G --> H[Redirect to Dashboard]
    B -->|Yes| H
    H --> I[API calls with Bearer token]
    I --> J{Token valid?}
    J -->|Yes| K[Return data]
    J -->|No 401| L[Logout → Login]
